662real_T rt_powd_snf(real_T u0, real_T u1)



663{



664  real_T tmp;



665  real_T tmp_0;



666  real_T y;



667  if (rtIsNaN(u0) || rtIsNaN(u1)) {



668    y = (rtNaN);



669  } else {



670    tmp = fabs(u0);



671    tmp_0 = fabs(u1);



672    if (rtIsInf(u1)) {



673      if (tmp == 1.0) {



674        y = 1.0;



675      } else if (tmp > 1.0) {



676        if (u1 > 0.0) {



677          y = (rtInf);



678        } else {



679          y = 0.0;



680        }



681      } else if (u1 > 0.0) {



682        y = 0.0;



683      } else {



684        y = (rtInf);



685      }



686    } else if (tmp_0 == 0.0) {



687      y = 1.0;



688    } else if (tmp_0 == 1.0) {



689      if (u1 > 0.0) {



690        y = u0;



691      } else {



692        y = 1.0 / u0;



693      }



694    } else if (u1 == 2.0) {



695      y = u0 * u0;



696    } else if ((u1 == 0.5) && (u0 >= 0.0)) {



697      y = sqrt(u0);



698    } else if ((u0 < 0.0) && (u1 > floor(u1))) {



699      y = (rtNaN);



700    } else {



701      y = pow(u0, u1);



702    }



703  }



704



705  return y;



706}

1467static void ap_LUf_boolean_Tint32_Treal32_T(real32_T outU[], real32_T outP[],



1468  int32_T N, boolean_T outS[])



1469{



1470  /* S-Function (sdsplu2): '<S211>/LU Factorization' */



1471  /* initialize status output */



1472  outS[0U] = false;



1473



1474  /* initialize row-pivot indices */



1475  app_B.k = 0;



1476  while (app_B.k < N) {



1477    outP[app_B.k] = (real32_T)(app_B.k + 1);



1478    app_B.k++;



1479  }



1480



1481  app_B.k = 0;



1482  while (app_B.k < N) {



1483    app_B.p = app_B.k;



1484



1485    /* Scan the lower triangular part of this column only. */



1486    /* Record row of largest value */



1487    app_B.idx1_tmp = app_B.k * N;



1488    app_B.mTmp1 = outU[app_B.idx1_tmp + app_B.k];



1489    if (app_B.mTmp1 < 0.0F) {



1490      app_B.mTmp1 = -app_B.mTmp1;



1491    }



1492



1493    app_B.r = app_B.k + 1;



1494    while (app_B.r < N) {



1495      app_B.mTmp2 = outU[app_B.idx1_tmp + app_B.r];



1496      if (app_B.mTmp2 < 0.0F) {



1497        app_B.mTmp2 = -app_B.mTmp2;



1498      }



1499



1500      if (app_B.mTmp2 > app_B.mTmp1) {



1501        app_B.p = app_B.r;



1502        app_B.mTmp1 = app_B.mTmp2;



1503      }



1504



1505      app_B.r++;



1506    }



1507



1508    /* swap rows if required */



1509    if (app_B.p != app_B.k) {



1510      app_B.c = 0;



1511      while (app_B.c < N) {



1512        app_B.idx1 = app_B.c * N;



1513        app_B.r = app_B.idx1 + app_B.p;



1514        app_B.mTmp1 = outU[app_B.r];



1515        app_B.i_n = app_B.idx1 + app_B.k;



1516        outU[app_B.r] = outU[app_B.i_n];



1517        outU[app_B.i_n] = app_B.mTmp1;



1518        app_B.c++;



1519      }



1520



1521      /* swap pivot row indices */



1522      app_B.mTmp1 = outP[app_B.p];



1523      outP[app_B.p] = outP[app_B.k];



1524      outP[app_B.k] = app_B.mTmp1;



1525    }



1526



1527    app_B.idx1 = app_B.k * N + app_B.k;



1528    if (outU[app_B.idx1] == 0.0F) {



1529      outS[0U] = true;



1530    } else {



1531      app_B.r = app_B.k + 1;



1532      while (app_B.r < N) {



1533        app_B.i_n = app_B.idx1_tmp + app_B.r;



1534        outU[app_B.i_n] /= outU[app_B.idx1];



1535        app_B.r++;



1536      }



1537



1538      app_B.c = app_B.k + 1;



1539      while (app_B.c < N) {



1540        app_B.idx1 = app_B.c * N;



1541        app_B.r = app_B.k + 1;



1542        while (app_B.r < N) {



1543          app_B.i_n = app_B.idx1 + app_B.r;



1544          outU[app_B.i_n] -= outU[app_B.idx1_tmp + app_B.r] * outU[app_B.idx1 +



1545            app_B.k];



1546          app_B.r++;



1547        }



1548



1549        app_B.c++;



1550      }



1551    }



1552



1553    app_B.k++;



1554  }



1555



1556  /* End of S-Function (sdsplu2): '<S211>/LU Factorization' */



1557}

1559static real_T app_rt_powd_snf(real_T u0, real_T u1)



1560{



1561  real_T y;



1562  if (rtIsNaN(u0) || rtIsNaN(u1)) {



1563    y = (rtNaN);



1564  } else {



1565    app_B.d = fabs(u0);
